# The Pulse

Production branch is **pulse_cdm**

Staging branch is **c4c.staging**

## Deploying:
development (deploy branch c4c.dev on github to moose.powertohange.com):

    cap c4c2/dev deploy

staging (deploy branch c4c.staging on github to emu.powertochange.com):

    cap c4c2/staging deploy

production (deploy branch pulse_cdm on github to pulse.powertochange.com):

    cap deploy target=prod

### Roll-back to previous deploy:
(you may only be able to do this once)

development:

    cap c4c2/dev deploy:rollback

staging:

    cap c4c2/staging deploy:rollback

production:

    cap deploy:rollback target=prod

## Restart server (via Passenger):

    touch tmp/restart.txt